response.overview: Now the whole family can squeal with laughter at this brand new show Twin Squeaks. If you're the sort of person who wants to know what happens when you get your head stuck in a giant pencil sharpener, what's the most respectful thing to do when your local librarian dies and what exactly has the camel got to do with it all anyway, 1) you should get out more and 2) you should Buy this video!  Alongside classic Joe " I know a song that will...", here's your first chance to see the "Hypno-Club of Caractacus", the "Blade of Bubble-Onia" and the long lost "Ancient Chopper of Haemerroydia".  Warning: If you understand every moment of this video, get professional help immediately!  "The guy only has to open his mouth and I star laughing" Joe's dentist.
response.title: Joe Pasqaule: Twin Squeaks
